# Skills to skip when running `make link`.
# One name per line. Names match either a top-level catalog skill (e.g. `shadcn-ui`)
# or a bundle-expanded sub-skill (e.g. `shadcn`, `frontend-design`).
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored.
#
# Maintain with:
#   make ignore-skill   SKILL=<name>   # add + unlink now
#   make unignore-skill SKILL=<name>   # remove; next `make link` will re-link
superpowers
